 SUBROUTINE CROTG ( CA , CB , C , S )
 COMPLEX CA , CB , S
 REAL C
 COMPLEX ALPHA
 REAL NORM , SCALE
 INTRINSIC CABS , CONJG , SQRT
 IF ( CABS ( CA ) .EQ. 0. ) THEN
 C = 0.
 S = ( 1. , 0. )
 CA = CB
 ELSE
 SCALE = CABS ( CA ) + CABS ( CB )
 NORM = SCALE * SQRT ( ( CABS ( CA / SCALE ) ) ** 2 + ( CABS ( CB / SCALE ) ) ** 2 )
 ALPHA = CA / CABS ( CA )
 C = CABS ( CA ) / NORM
 S = ALPHA * CONJG ( CB ) / NORM
 CA = ALPHA * NORM
 END IF
 RETURN
 END
